    • Constructor Detail

      • ArrangementGroupingComponent

        public ArrangementGroupingComponent(CompositeArrangementSettingsToken token,
                                    ArrangementColorsProvider colorsProvider,
                                    ArrangementStandardSettingsManager settingsManager)
                             throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Assumes that given token has no children or all its children have the same UI role.

        Lays out given token (and its children if any) in a single row.

        Parameters:
        token - base token which serves as a grouping rule model
        colorsProvider - colors provider
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if invariant described above is not satisfied
